*Mlade* su želele da sve bude po njihovom ukusu. (The young people wanted everything to be according to their taste.)

Često se *mlade* upuste u neke avanture. (Young people often embark on some adventures.)

Ona je odrastala sa *mladima* iz susedstva. (She grew up with young people from the neighbourhood.)

*Mladim* ljudima je teško da se snađu u životu. (Young people find it hard to make their way in life.)

Njegove *mlade* godine su mu doneli mnogo sreće. (His young years have brought him a lot of luck.)